data.name: Description.Text
data.value: > This project is built on Visual studio [Winforms] using C# language. >It generates random solvable mazes and solves them in realtime. >User can select the size of the maze and a starting point for the maze generation to begin , the end point is the bottom right cell. >We use the concept of Depth First Algorithm (DFS) to both generate and solve mazes.
